{"tid":1786681,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[突發]12月21日和你Christmas Shop 2.0活動竟然取消咗","createTime":"2019-12-17T10:05:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-18T09:47:54.000Z","uid":287028,"like":148,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":62,"replies":[{"pid":"243f9f6e438f7c72d15c488921b0a3cfadc710e9","tid":1786681,"uid":287028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T10:05:36.000Z","msg":"我琴晚發咗個好奇怪嘅夢。 我夢見自己一個人約咗朋友<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>2點鍾</strong></span>去<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">海港城Shopping</span></strong>。 唔知點解個商場越黎越多人，而且<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>個個都戴曬口罩</strong></span>，但<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">無人著黑色衫</span></strong>，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">無人叫口號。</span></strong> 多人到<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">塞住所有出入口</span></strong>完全行唔到。 我於是問吓企我隔離個女仔今日做咩咁多人，佢都唔知，不過佢話佢都係等緊朋友。 結果我<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">等到商場閂門</span></strong>我朋友都未黎。 於是我唯有約我朋友去<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">另一個商場</span></strong>等。 <br />\n<br />\n之後我醒咗先知原來我發緊夢😯<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wA0vqBJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwA0vqBJ.jpg&h=e90b50c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n由於Telegram群組話活動已取消，我請大家唔好再<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">廣傳下面呢個group link</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/Nd-f9lZBFn-K9aSVNuGlDA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FNd-f9lZBFn-K9aSVNuGlDA&d=oGSqBYpvdEZZERTBUGrA0n8q8VOs0%2BPBwwlvB7nX800%3D&h=3b5890bd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/Nd-f9lZBFn-K9aSVNuGlDA</a>"},{"pid":"4fc276874f64fb1cb6360f9afedbc332622ba7d2","tid":1786681,"uid":163704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T10:05:53.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n[你今日FC咗未] 全港最大的Fact Check平台已經推出了<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1776631\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1776631</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"p